	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.455, and Index, 634, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.502-511, no. 494, 42 B.C. With L. Livineius Regulus, P. Clodius M. f., and L. Mussidius T. f. Longus as IIIIviri.\n" .
