	dprr:hasNoteText "IIIIvir A. P. F. In MRR 2.447, Index, 594, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.502- 511, no. 494, 42 B.C. With L. Livineius, P. Clodius, and C. Vibius Varus. See Wiseman, NM 243, no. 268.\n" .
